# UI — shadcn/ui (Hard Rule)

- Primitives (Button, Input, Textarea, Card, Dialog): shadcn only; add with `npx shadcn@latest add <component>`. Live in `components/ui/`; compose in `components/chat/`, `components/layout/`. Tailwind for style; presentational only. No other UI lib for buttons/inputs/cards.
